Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF) Metrics stores logs, metrics data, and event data from apps running on PCF for the past two weeks.
It graphically presents this data to help operators and developers better understand the health and performance of their apps.

## What's New in PCF Metrics v1.5

In addition to the out-of-the-box features provided in previous versions, PCF Metrics v1.5 introduces the following new functionality:

* Streaming metrics visualization
* Alerting and monitoring for metrics and events
* Architectural updates that improve reliability while reducing the overall infrastructure footprint

